<view class="page hall">
  <view class="head" style="padding-top: {{navTop}}px;">
    <text class="title" style="height: {{navHeight}}px; line-height: {{navHeight}}px;">预约预订</text>
    <text class="subtitle">提前预约，尊享最佳体验</text>
  </view>

  <view class="booking-list">
    <view class="type-card" bindtap="goStay">
      <view class="card-hero stay">
        <view class="hero-icon"><t-icon name="home" size="142rpx" /></view>
        <text class="hero-text">山居夜宿</text>
      </view>
      <view class="card-body">
        <text class="card-title">住宿预订</text>
        <text class="card-desc">七间雅室，各具风情。春悦、夏舍、秋得、冬裕……每一扇窗都是一幅山水画卷。</text>
        <view class="tags">
          <text class="tag">春悦 · 亲子房</text>
          <text class="tag">夏舍 · 大床房</text>
          <text class="tag">秋得 · 标准间</text>
          <text class="tag">冬裕 · 榻榻米</text>
        </view>
        <view class="arrow-row"><text>查看详情</text><t-icon name="chevron-right" size="26rpx" /></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="type-card" bindtap="goDining">
      <view class="card-hero dining">
        <view class="hero-icon"><t-icon name="fork" size="142rpx" /></view>
        <text class="hero-text">雅阁飨宴</text>
      </view>
      <view class="card-body">
        <text class="card-title">用餐预订</text>
        <text class="card-desc">四间古典餐厅，各具韵致。兮古、栖鹿、梦堂、心语，在雅致空间中品味山间至味。</text>
        <view class="tags">
          <text class="tag">兮古 · 6-10人</text>
          <text class="tag">栖鹿 · 8-12人</text>
          <text class="tag">梦堂 · 8-12人</text>
          <text class="tag">心语 · 8-12人</text>
        </view>
        <view class="arrow-row"><text>查看详情</text><t-icon name="chevron-right" size="26rpx" /></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="type-card" data-type="空间预订" bindtap="consult">
      <view class="card-hero space">
        <view class="hero-icon"><t-icon name="teahouse" size="142rpx" /></view>
        <text class="hero-text">雅室清谈</text>
      </view>
      <view class="card-body">
        <text class="card-title">空间预订</text>
        <text class="card-desc">会议室、禅修室、VIP茶室、展厅，可用于小型雅集、课程、会谈与静修。</text>
        <view class="tags">
          <text class="tag">多功能会议室</text>
          <text class="tag">禅修室</text>
          <text class="tag">VIP茶室</text>
          <text class="tag">展厅</text>
        </view>
        <view class="arrow-row"><text>咨询预订</text><t-icon name="chevron-right" size="26rpx" /></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="type-card" data-type="包场预订" bindtap="consult">
      <view class="card-hero event">
        <view class="hero-icon"><t-icon name="calendar-event" size="142rpx" /></view>
        <text class="hero-text">山居包场</text>
      </view>
      <view class="card-body">
        <text class="card-title">举办活动</text>
        <text class="card-desc">适合企业团建、私享茶会、主题沙龙、禅修课程等包场活动，按需求定制方案。</text>
        <view class="tags">
          <text class="tag">全场包场</text>
          <text class="tag">茶会沙龙</text>
          <text class="tag">企业团建</text>
          <text class="tag">课程活动</text>
        </view>
        <view class="arrow-row"><text>咨询方案</text><t-icon name="chevron-right" size="26rpx" /></view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tips">
    <text class="tips-title">✦ 温馨提示</text>
    <view class="tip"><text class="bullet">·</text><text>建议提前预订，确保心仪的房间与时段</text></view>
    <view class="tip"><text class="bullet">·</text><text>会员享受专属优惠政策</text></view>
    <view class="tip"><text class="bullet">·</text><text>如需取消，请提前 24 小时联系</text></view>
    <view class="tip"><text class="bullet">·</text><text>到店支付，支持微信 / 支付宝 / 现金</text></view>
  </view>
</view>
